      "comment": "HAVEYOUMETTED (1) hasn't been disgraced from much wider barriers of late including a placing at this circuit and distance three back. The ace draw gives him every chance to produce his best form. UNDER THE ALTA (9) draws wide again but was very good when he led from a similar draw at this circuit and distance on Tuesday and went on to score by 6 metres. Could back that up. BY GEE BY JINGO (6) was held up and broke when only 4.6 metres from the winner last start. Has been back to the trials since. Chance with manners. ME FLASH (8) draws out but with even luck may feature after finishing third at Bunbury last time out.",
